      <title>希思罗机场说，停电关闭后，它已经完全运行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/london-heathrow-airport-lhr-closed-due-to-power-outage-caused-by-fire-m8jusd2c</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦希思罗机场（Heathrow Airport）表示，在史无前例的日停电后，它是开放和全部运营的，这使旅行在欧洲最繁忙的机场中待了数十万乘客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/london-heathrow-airport-lhr-closed-due-to-power-outage-caused-by-fire-m8jusd2c</guid>
