    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希思罗机场停电暴露了机场电源中的弱点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/heathrow-blackout-exposes-weak-spot-in-airport-s-power-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦希思罗机场（London Heathrow）在周五的前所未有的停电使该机场对潜在脆弱的基础设施的依赖焦点，而英国最大的枢纽正在游说雄心勃勃的扩张计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/heathrow-blackout-exposes-weak-spot-in-airport-s-power-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
