      <title>欧盟国家推动对气体存储目标的市场状况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/eu-nations-push-to-factor-market-conditions-in-gas-storage-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果市场价格过度增加补给储量的成本，则欧盟成员国正在推动在未来两年内偏离天然气储存目标的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/eu-nations-push-to-factor-market-conditions-in-gas-storage-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 22:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
